    hh3cTransceiverChannelCurRXPower OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX      Integer32
        MAX-ACCESS  read-only
        STATUS      current
        DESCRIPTION
            "Indicating the current received power.
            The unit is in hundredths of dBm."
