    hh3cTransceiverChannelTemperature OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX      Integer32
        MAX-ACCESS  read-only
        STATUS      current
        DESCRIPTION
            "Indicating the current temperature.
            The unit is Celsius centigrade."
