    hh3cTransceiverChannelBiasCurrent OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX      Integer32
        MAX-ACCESS  read-only
        STATUS      current
        DESCRIPTION
            "Indicating the current bias electric current.
            The unit is in hundredths of mA."
