    hh3cTransceiverChanCurCD   OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX      Integer32
        MAX-ACCESS  read-only
        STATUS      current
        DESCRIPTION
            "Current chromatic dispersion, in hundredths of a picosecond per nanometer."
