    hh3cTransceiverChanCDAvg   OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX      Integer32
        MAX-ACCESS  read-only
        STATUS      current
        DESCRIPTION
            "Average chromatic dispersion value within the statistical period,
            in hundredths of a picosecond per nanometer."
