    hh3cTransceiverChanEsnrAvg    OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX      Integer32
        MAX-ACCESS  read-only
        STATUS      current
        DESCRIPTION
            "Average signal-to-noise ratio of electrical signals during the statistical period,
